#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using Hibernate Reactive"
msgstr "使用 Hibernate Reactive"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"无法保证此扩展程序的向后兼容性及其在生态系统中的可用性\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">预览</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"link:https://hibernate.org/reactive/[Hibernate Reactive] is a reactive API for Hibernate ORM, supporting non-blocking database drivers\n"
"and a reactive style of interaction with the database."
msgstr "link:https://hibernate.org/reactive/[Hibernate Reactive] 是 Hibernate ORM 的一款响应式 API，支持非阻塞数据库驱动程序，并提供响应式风格的数据库交互方式。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hibernate Reactive is not a replacement for xref:hibernate-orm.adoc[Hibernate ORM] or the future of Hibernate ORM.\n"
"It is a different stack tailored for reactive use cases where you need high-concurrency."
msgstr "Hibernate Reactive 并非 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc[Hibernate ORM] 的替代品，也不是 Hibernate ORM 的未来发展方向。它是一个专为需要高并发性的响应式用例量身定制的独立技术栈。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Also, using Quarkus REST (formerly RESTEasy Reactive), our default REST layer, does not require the use of Hibernate Reactive.\n"
"It is perfectly valid to use Quarkus REST with Hibernate ORM,\n"
"and if you do not need high-concurrency, or are not accustomed to the reactive paradigm, it is recommended to use Hibernate ORM."
msgstr "此外，使用 Quarkus REST（原名 RESTEasy Reactive）——我们的默认 REST 层——并不需要使用 Hibernate Reactive。 将 Quarkus REST 与 Hibernate ORM 结合使用是完全可行的，如果您不需要高并发，或者不习惯响应式范式，建议使用 Hibernate ORM。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hibernate Reactive works with the same annotations and most of the configuration described in the\n"
"xref:hibernate-orm.adoc[Hibernate ORM guide]. This guide will only focus on what's specific\n"
"for Hibernate Reactive."
msgstr "Hibernate Reactive 采用与《 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc[Hibernate ORM 指南] 》中所述相同的注解以及大部分配置。本指南将仅重点介绍 Hibernate Reactive 的特有内容。"

