#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Clone the Git repository: `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}`, or download an {quickstarts-archive-url}[archive]."
msgstr "克隆 Git 仓库： `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}` ，或下载 {quickstarts-archive-url}[存档]。"

