#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"%prod.quarkus.datasource.reactive.url=postgresql:///your_database\n"
"%prod.quarkus.datasource.jdbc.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/hibernate_orm_test"
msgstr "%prod.quarkus.datasource.reactive.url=postgresql:///your_database %prod.quarkus.datasource.jdbc.url=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/hibernate_orm_test"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The presence of the JDBC driver will enable Hibernate ORM. If you want to disable it, and only use Hibernate Reactive, you can use:"
msgstr "如果安装了 JDBC 驱动程序，将启用 Hibernate ORM。如果您想禁用它，仅使用 Hibernate Reactive，可以使用以下方法："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus will set many Hibernate Reactive configuration settings automatically, and will often use more modern defaults."
msgstr "Quarkus 会自动设置许多 Hibernate Reactive 的配置选项，并且通常会采用更现代的默认值。"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "CDI integration"
msgstr "CDI 集成"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are familiar with using Hibernate Reactive in Quarkus, you probably already have injected the `Mutiny.SessionFactory` using CDI:"
msgstr "如果您熟悉在 Quarkus 中使用 Hibernate Reactive，那么您很可能已经通过 CDI 注入了 `Mutiny.SessionFactory` ："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This will inject the `Mutiny.SessionFactory` of the default persistence unit."
msgstr "这将注入默认持久化单元的 `Mutiny.SessionFactory` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Prior to Quarkus 3.0 it was also possible to inject a `@RequestScoped` bean for `Mutiny.Session`. However, the lifecycle of a reactive session does not fit the lifecycle of the CDI request context. Therefore, this bean is removed in Quarkus 3.0."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 3.0 之前，也可以为 `Mutiny.Session` 注入一个 `@RequestScoped 范围的` Bean。然而，响应式会话的生命周期与 CDI 请求上下文的生命周期并不匹配。因此，该 Bean 在 Quarkus 3.0 中已被移除。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Activate/deactivate persistence units"
msgstr "激活/停用持久化单元"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When a persistence unit is configured at build time, and it is assigned entity types or an xref:datasource.adoc#datasource-active[active datasource], the persistence unit is active by default.\n"
"Quarkus starts the corresponding Hibernate Reactive `SessionFactory` when the application starts."
msgstr "如果在构建时配置了持久化单元，并且为其分配了实体类型或 xref:datasource.adoc#datasource-active[活动数据源] ，则该持久化单元默认处于活动状态。Quarkus 会在应用程序启动时启动相应的 Hibernate Reactive `SessionFactory` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To deactivate a persistence unit at runtime, see xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#persistence-unit-active[the corresponding section of the Hibernate ORM guide]."
msgstr "若要在运行时停用持久化单元，请参阅 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#persistence-unit-active[《Hibernate ORM 指南》中的相关章节] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you decide to follow the example from the Hibernate ORM guide to declare a custom CDI bean for the active persistence unit,\n"
"but you use Hibernate Reactive,\n"
"make sure to work with the `Mutiny.SessionFactory` type instead of `Session`:\n"
"this is one way Hibernate Reactive's API entrypoint differs from Hibernate ORM's."
msgstr "如果您决定参照 Hibernate ORM 指南中的示例，为活动持久化单元声明一个自定义 CDI Bean，但您使用的是 Hibernate Reactive，请务必使用 `Mutiny.SessionFactory` 类型，而不是 `Session` ：这是 Hibernate Reactive 的 API 入口点与 Hibernate ORM 不同之处之一。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See <<hr-cdi-integration>> for details."
msgstr "详情请参见 <<hr-cdi-integration>> 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Automatically transitioning to Flyway to Manage Schemas"
msgstr "自动切换到 Flyway 来管理模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hibernate Reactive can be used in the same application as Flyway.\n"
"See xref:flyway.adoc#reactive-datasources[this section of the Flyway extension documentation]\n"
"for details regarding configuration of Flyway in a reactive application."
msgstr "Hibernate Reactive 可以与 Flyway 在同一个应用程序中使用。有关在响应式应用程序中配置 Flyway 的详细信息，请参阅 xref:flyway.adoc#reactive-datasources[Flyway 扩展文档的这一部分] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
