#, fuzzy
msgid "Testing"
msgstr "测试"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using Hibernate Reactive in a `@QuarkusTest` is slightly more involved than using Hibernate ORM due to the asynchronous nature of the APIs and the fact that all operations need to run on a Vert.x Event Loop."
msgstr "在 `@QuarkusTest` 中使用 Hibernate Reactive 比使用 Hibernate ORM 稍显复杂，这是因为其 API 具有异步特性，且所有操作都需要在 Vert.x 事件循环上运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Two components are necessary to write these tests:"
msgstr "编写这些测试需要两个组成部分："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The use of `@io.quarkus.test.vertx.RunOnVertxContext` or `@io.quarkus.test.TestReactiveTransaction` on the test methods"
msgstr "在测试方法中使用 `@io.quarkus.test.vertx.RunOnVertxContext` 或 `@io.quarkus.test.TestReactiveTransaction`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The use of `io.quarkus.test.vertx.UniAsserter` as a test method parameter."
msgstr "将 `io.quarkus.test.vertx.UniAsserter` 用作测试方法的参数。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "These classes are provided by the `quarkus-test-vertx` dependency."
msgstr "这些类由 `quarkus-test-vertx` 依赖项提供。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A very simple example usage looks like:"
msgstr "一个非常简单的用法示例如下："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See the Javadoc of `UniAsserter` for a full description of the various methods that can be used for creating assertions."
msgstr "有关可用于创建断言的各种方法的完整说明，请参阅 `UniAsserter` 的 Javadoc。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can also extend the `io.quarkus.test.vertx.UniAsserterInterceptor` to wrap the injected `UniAsserter` and customize the default behavior. For example, the interceptor can be used to execute the assert methods within a separate database transaction.:"
msgstr "您还可以扩展 `io.quarkus.test.vertx.UniAsserterInterceptor，以` 封装注入的 `UniAsserter` 并自定义默认行为。例如，可以使用该拦截器在单独的数据库事务中执行断言方法："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Multiple persistence units"
msgstr "多个持久化单元"

#. type: Title ===
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Setting up multiple persistence units"
msgstr "配置多个持久化单元"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In a similar fashion to Hibernate ORM, Hibernate Reactive supports multiple persistence units."
msgstr "与 Hibernate ORM 类似，Hibernate Reactive 也支持多个持久化单元。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can define multiple persistence units and datasources, and they can mix blocking and reactive datasources.\n"
"To ensure that a datasource supports reactive, you need to set the `reactive` property to `true`."
msgstr "您可以定义多个持久化单元和数据源，并且这些数据源可以同时包含阻塞型和响应式数据源。要确保某个数据源支持响应式模式，您需要将 `reactive` 属性设置为 `true` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Define a reactive datasource named `users`."
msgstr "定义一个名为 `users` 的响应式数据源。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Define a reactive datasource named `inventory`."
msgstr "定义一个名为 `inventory 的` 响应式数据源。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Define a persistence unit named `users` and specify the datasource."
msgstr "定义一个名为 `users 的` 持久化单元，并指定数据源。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Define a persistence unit named `inventory` and specify the datasource."
msgstr "定义一个名为 `inventory 的` 持久化单元，并指定数据源。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When using named persistence units, you must set the `datasource` property to the name of the corresponding datasource."
msgstr "使用命名持久化单元时，必须将 `datasource` 属性设置为相应数据源的名称。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Limitations and other things you should know"
msgstr "限制及其他注意事项"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus does not modify the libraries it uses; this rule applies to Hibernate Reactive as well: when using\n"
"this extension you will mostly have the same experience as using the original library."
msgstr "Quarkus 不会修改其所使用的库；这一规则同样适用于 Hibernate Reactive：使用该扩展时，您的使用体验将与使用原始库时基本一致。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But while they share the same code, Quarkus does configure some components automatically and inject custom implementations\n"
"for some extension points; this should be transparent and useful but if you're an expert of Hibernate Reactive you might want to\n"
"know what is being done."
msgstr "尽管它们使用相同的代码，但 Quarkus 会自动配置某些组件，并为某些扩展点注入自定义实现；这一过程应是透明且有用的，但如果你是 Hibernate Reactive 的专家，可能希望了解具体做了哪些操作。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here's a list of things to pay attention when using Hibernate Reactive in Quarkus:"
msgstr "以下是在 Quarkus 中使用 Hibernate Reactive 时需要注意的事项列表："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hibernate Reactive is not configurable via a `persistence.xml` file."
msgstr "Hibernate Reactive 无法通过 `persistence.xml` 文件进行配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This extension only considers the default persistence unit at the moment:\n"
"it's not possible to configure multiple persistence units,\n"
"or even a single named persistence unit."
msgstr "目前，该扩展仅支持默认的持久化单元：无法配置多个持久化单元，甚至无法配置单个命名持久化单元。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This extension does not support xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#database-approach[database-based multitenancy]\n"
"or xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#schema-approach[schema-based multitenancy] at the moment.\n"
"xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#discriminator-approach[Discriminator-based multitenancy], on the other hand, is expected to work correctly.\n"
"See https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/15959."
msgstr "目前，该扩展不支持 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#database-approach[基于数据库的多租户模式] ，也不支持 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#schema-approach[基于模式的多租户模式] 。不过， xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#discriminator-approach[基于区分符的多租户模式] 预计能够正常工作。请参阅 https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/issues/15959 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Integration with the Envers extension is not supported."
msgstr "不支持与 Envers 扩展的集成。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Transaction demarcation cannot be done using `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` or `QuarkusTransaction`;\n"
"if you use xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc[Hibernate Reactive with Panache],\n"
"consider xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc#transactions[using `@WithTransaction` or `Panache.withTransaction()`] instead."
msgstr "无法使用 `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` 或 `QuarkusTransaction` 来划分事务；如果您 xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc[在 Panache 中] 使用 xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc[Hibernate Reactive] ，请考虑 xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc#transactions[改用@WithTransaction或Panache.withTransaction()] 。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Simplifying Hibernate Reactive with Panache"
msgstr "以独特风格简化 Hibernate Reactive"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc[Hibernate Reactive with Panache] extension facilitates the usage of Hibernate Reactive\n"
"by providing active record style entities (and repositories) and focuses on making your entities trivial and fun to write in Quarkus."
msgstr "xref:hibernate-reactive-panache.adoc[“Hibernate Reactive with Panache] ” 扩展通过提供活动记录风格的实体（及存储库），简化了 Hibernate Reactive 的使用，并致力于让开发者在 Quarkus 中编写实体变得简单且充满乐趣。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Validation modes and Hibernate Validator integration"
msgstr "验证模式与 Hibernate Validator 的集成"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To find out more on how the <<quarkus-hibernate-orm_quarkus-hibernate-orm-validation-mode,`quarkus.hibernate-orm.validation.mode` configuration property>>.\n"
"influence your Hibernate Reactive application see the xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#validator_integration[corresponding Hibernate ORM guide],\n"
"as these modes work the same in both cases."
msgstr "如需进一步了解 xref:quarkus-hibernate-orm_quarkus-hibernate-orm-validation-mode[quarkus.hibernate-orm.validation.mode配置属性] 如何影响您的 Hibernate Reactive 应用程序，请参阅 xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#validator_integration[相应的 Hibernate ORM 指南，] 因为这两种模式在两种情况下都具有相同的运作方式。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Configuration Reference for Hibernate Reactive"
msgstr "Hibernate Reactive 配置参考"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You will notice that some properties\n"
"contain \"jdbc\" in their name: this is because Hibernate ORM refers to its \"data access\" layer as \"JDBC\" for historical reasons. Hibernate Reactive uses Vert.x Reactive SQL clients for its data access layer rather than JDBC."
msgstr "你会注意到，某些属性的名称中包含“jdbc”：这是因为出于历史原因，Hibernate ORM 将其“数据访问”层称为“JDBC”。Hibernate Reactive 采用 Vert.x Reactive SQL 客户端作为其数据访问层，而非 JDBC。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Regardless of their name, these properties still make sense for Hibernate Reactive."
msgstr "无论名称如何，这些属性对于 Hibernate Reactive 来说仍然是有意义的。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/hibernate-reactive.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<span class=\"icon\"><i class=\"fa fa-lock\" title=\"Fixed at build time\"></i></span> Configuration property fixed at build time - All other configuration properties are overridable at runtime <input type=\"search\" id=\"config-search-0\" placeholder=\"FILTER CONFIGURATION\" disabled>"
msgstr "<span class=\"icon\"><i class=\"fa fa-lock\" title=\"在构建时固定\"></i></span> 配置属性在构建时已固定 - 所有其他配置属性均可在运行时覆盖 <input type=\"search\" id=\"config-search-0\" placeholder=\"过滤配置\" disabled>"
